{"title":"Week in Review – January 19th, 2025","link":"https://www.dcrainmaker.com/2025/01/week-review-january-19-2025.html","date":1737299866000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Weekinreview.jpeg\" src=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/12/Weekinreview.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"718\" height=\"478\" srcset=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/12/Weekinreview.jpeg 718w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/12/Weekinreview-200x133.jpeg 200w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/12/Weekinreview-300x200.jpeg 300w\" /></p>\n<p>The Week in Review is a collection of both all the goodness I’ve written during the past week around the internet, as well as a small pile of links I found interesting – generally endurance sports related. I’ve often wondered what to do with all of the coolness that people write, and while I share a lot of it on <a href=\"https://x.com/dcrainmakerblog\">Twitter/X</a> and <a href=\"https://bsky.app/profile/dcrainmaker.com\">BlueSky</a>, this is a better forum for sending it on to y’all. Most times these different streams don’t overlap, so be on the lookout at all these places for good stuff!</p>\n<p>So with that, let’s get into the action!</p>\n<h3><strong><span>DCR Posts In The Past Week:</span></strong></h3>\n<p>Here’s all the latest posts on the site:</p>\n<p><strong>Sunday:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.dcrainmaker.com/2025/01/fit-file-instinct-3-instinct-e-amazfit-ces-fun.html\">FIT File: Garmin Instinct 3…Let’s Chat</a><br />\n<strong>Tuesday:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.dcrainmaker.com/2025/01/garmin-instinct3-vs-garmin-fenix8-very-detailed-review.html\">Garmin Instinct 3 vs Garmin Fenix 8: Every Difference Detailed!</a><br />\n<strong>Thursday:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.dcrainmaker.com/2025/01/garmin-ecg-now-available-in-eu-australia.html\">Garmin ECG Now Available in EU (But not Fenix 7 Pro &amp; Epix Pro)</a></p>\n<p>Stay tuned for the final Instinct 3 review this week, following me putting it through the paces the past few weeks, including a <a href=\"https://www.strava.com/activities/13364754057\">60KM trek this past Wednesday</a>. Atop that, there’s a smattering of smaller company news I want to catch-up on, and one moderately-sized announcement this week coming up. Maybe more, who knows.</p>\n<h3><span><strong>Sports Tech Deals:</strong></span></h3>\n<p>Some new ones have popped up this past week. I think the Fenix 7 at $429 is probably the most interesting for people eyeing that new Instinct 3, since this is basically cheaper while having more features. I’ll continue sweeping and adding in a few more of these later tonight, so keep checking back.</p>\n<table>\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th></th><th><span>Product</span></th><th><span>Sale Price</span></th><th><span>Amazon</span></th><th><span>Sale Notes</span></th>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</thead>\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td><a href=\"https://www.dcrainmaker.com/2025/01/amazfit-t-rex-3-gps-watch-depth-review.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img width=\"200\" height=\"211\" src=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/11/AmazFitT-Rex3Transparent-200x211.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/11/AmazFitT-Rex3Transparent-200x211.png 200w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/11/AmazFitT-Rex3Transparent-720x760.png 720w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/11/AmazFitT-Rex3Transparent.png 1316w\" /></a></td><td><a href=\"https://www.dcrainmaker.com/2025/01/amazfit-t-rex-3-gps-watch-depth-review.html\" target=\"_blank\">AmazFit T-Rex 3 - $45 off</a></td><td>$234</td><td><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Amazfit-Military-Privacy-Offline-Water-Resistant/dp/B0DCZ9PRCP?crid=KEM3NOVWFW13&amp;dib=eyJ2IjoiMSJ9.CKiK0uww2yn4qa00hejwZ62DrtTI_v2gH33aO08WFvPXo8c7STk1OzqFLHOzC8RIxPMxbjKZz_U0ycKztmn7XDAxCcMKn0_z2EBpTKZOpuuN9kxHDAmZGDEfunzp7rMcH_4cSByMKFdTs17r3d9axFsxQCYOqYcZXLhD9Na6zDVSv-PHZppmijUW8_4wDocsPsJ1yf3YNCcrMXxj0RtFcCNWNz17HuqZ8C9PnQuc4GI.8aStIQQOgLqavd_d-EB6G4qHqCEWVa